NAME
     countalpha - counts the number of times the letters  a  -  z
     occur and computes a probability model.

SYNOPSIS
     countalpha file1 file2

DESCRIPTION
     This program counts the number  of  times  the  letters  a-z
     occur in file1 and computes a probability model.  The proba-
     bility model is written in file2.  The program does not dis-
     tinguish between upper and lower case letters.

     The program does not need any subroutines.


